  "type": "elizaosDailySummary",
  "title": "Daily Report - 2026-04-16",
  "categories": [
    {
      "title": "ElizaOS Community Discussion - April 16, 2026",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "Community members expressed frustration over ElizaOS token underperforming while the broader crypto market was rallying. Several users noted the token showed little to no upward movement compared to other coins. Odilitime acknowledged the token was up on a 24-hour basis and encouraged celebrating small wins, while also noting the ElizaOS X account situation was in Twitter's hands.",
          "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1253563209462448241",
          "posters": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/posters/1776388934779-27x796.png"
        },
        {
          "text": "A heated debate broke out between community members regarding the project's direction. One user accused Shaw and the team of making false promises, failing to deliver revenue, and not communicating with the community. Another user pushed back, stating they were not misleading anyone and confirmed that ElizaOS v3 is almost ready, and the team is actively working on the Milady app and Eliza app. There was general agreement that communication from the team has been poor and that Shaw has not addressed the community directly about unmet promises.",
          "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1253563209462448241",
          "posters": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/posters/1776388956585-901lq.png"
        },
        {
          "text": "Multiple community members urged the team to publish a roadmap on the ElizaOS X account to build momentum, trust, and attention, especially given the favorable market conditions. Odilitime indicated the X account update was in Twitter's hands. Separately, Odilitime announced a discussion space about the limits of LLMs with some developers.",
          "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1253563209462448241",
          "posters": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/posters/1776388977790-culun7m.jpg"
        },
        {
          "text": "A new user asked about migrating their Ai16z tokens to Eliza after missing the deadline. Odilitime confirmed that migration is now closed and stated there was no workaround available.",
          "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1253563209462448241",
          "posters": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/posters/1776388997684-jzmnxf.jpg"
        },
        {
          "text": "A community member shared their participation in the BNB Chain Hackathon, building a value layer that automates alpha discovery and intelligent position building using ElizaOS. They requested votes on the DoraHacks platform as the project entered the judging phase with results expected in May.",
          "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1253563209462448241",
          "images": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/embed-thumbnail-1494404264745762877_a904f98d.jpg",
          "videos": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/elizaos-media/2044765545455886377_7e58903f.mp4"
        },
        {
          "text": "In the developer xfn-framework channel, Stan reported to Odilitime that the topup auto feature does not appear to be working on the cloud environment.",
          "sources": "https://discord.com/channels/1253563208833433701/1377726087789940836"
        }
      ],
      "topic": "discordrawdata"
    },
    {
      "title": "ElizaOS Development Activity: April 16, 2026",
      "content": {
        "text": "Development activity on April 16, 2026 centered on improving developer tooling consistency and expanding the plugin ecosystem. A key update involved standardizing linting processes in the Ollama plugin by replacing relative biome paths with bunx invocations, ensuring consistent execution across different environments. This change is captured in a pull request that is currently awaiting review. Additionally, a new plugin called megaswap-elizaos-plugin has been submitted to the elizaos-plugins registry and is currently in progress pending approval.",
        "sources": "https://elizaos.github.io/api/summaries/overall/day/2026-04-16.json",
        "posters": "https://cdn.elizaos.news/posters/1776389044610-6pfaun.jpg"
      },
      "topic": "miscellaneous"
    }
  ],
